Woodson said. "Houston is going to win a lot of games with him." 
</P>
<P>
 The Oilers stacked the line of scrimmage and it proved to be their downfall 
when Aikman hit Alvin Harper with a 53-yard touchdown pass in the third period 
for a 20-10 lead. Harper had single coverage on the play. 
</P>
