<P>
 Katella 
</P>
<P>
 Coach: Mike Cochrane (25th year). 
</P>
<P>
 1993: Third at the CIF State Division III finals; Southern Section II-A 
champions; Empire League champions; runners-up at Orange County Championships. 
</P>
<P>
 Key returners: Edgar Benitez, Jr.; Mike Lopez, Sr.; Erick Miramontes, Jr.; 
George Pinto, Jr.; Juan Venegas, Jr. 
</P>
<P>
