<DOCNO> LA091294-0220 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 078541 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 12, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 4; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
